Question: Dongguan Sunun Power Co., Ltd CES 2024 product highlight and specification
Summary:
Dongguan Sunun Power Co.,Ltd

Product: CES 2024 Power Supply Products

- AC adaptors
- Battery chargers
- USB wall chargers
- Open frame power supplies
- PD adapters
- Car chargers
- USB data cables

Dongguan Sunun Power Co., Ltd specializes in the development, manufacturing, and sales of power supply products. With over 10 years of experience, the company offers a range of products including AC adaptors, battery chargers, USB wall chargers, open frame power supplies, PD adapters, car chargers, and USB data cables. The company has two plants, one in Dongguan and the other in Shaoguan Guangdong, with a total of 8 finished production lines and a daily output of over 150,000 sets of power supply products. Their products have passed various quality system certifications and are well-received in both domestic and international markets, with customers including Amazon, AT&T, Hama, and more.
